metadata.name: New Age Bedroom R&B
metadata.description:
Vocalist and Producer Edwin, from the group PRETTYMUCH, takes a more electronic approach to R&B by utilizing saw waves and EDM style automation whilst still layering soulful vocals to redefine what it means to make R&B in your bedroom.  
  
Samples included in this Kit:  
 - ED 09 Hallows Master Demo F# Minor 86  
 - ED 08 Choly Master Demo C# Minor 142  
 - ED 10 Regular Master Demo C# Minor 95  
 - ED 01 Digitize Master Demo Eb Minor 140  
 - ED 07 Way Down Master Demo Gb Major 90  
 - ED 02 MELLOFI Master Demo E Minor 150  
 - ED 03 Pluckness Master Demo C# Minor 120  
 - ED 05 Foxy Master Demo Ab Major 156  
 - ED 06 Growing Master Demo C Minor 150  
 - ED 04 Complicated Master Demo Eb Minor 172
